== Job Parms ==

Job-specific parameters that affect all submitted jobs, but can be overridden on a node-by-node basis.
For more information, see [Scheduler Job Parms / Properties|/tops/schedulers#jobparms].

=== Commands ===

Pre Task Command:
    #id: rpfarm_pretaskcmd

    Specifies the command to run before executing the main task.

Post Task Command:
    #id: rpfarm_posttaskcmd

    Specifies the command to run after executing the main task.

=== Task Environment ===

Inherit Local Environment:
    #id: rpfarm_inheritlocalenv

    When on, the environment variables in the current session of PDG are copied into the task's environment.

Unset Variables:
    #id: rpfarm_envunset

    Specifies a space-separated list of environment variables that should be unset or removed from the scheduler's task environment.

Environment Variables:
    #id: rpfarm_envmulti

    Allows you to add custom environment variables to each task.

Houdini Max Threads:
    #id: rpfarm_usehoudinimaxthreads

    When on, sets the `HOUDINI_MAXTHREADS` environment to the specified value.

=== Advanced ===

Verbose Logging:
    #id: rpfarm_verbose

    When on, prints detailed output to console. Can be useful for debugging problems.

Warmup Paths:
    #id: rpfarm_warmuppaths

    Comma-separated list of file paths to pre-cache on pods before executing tasks. This can speed up initial task execution.

